SUMMARY:SALSA IN THE SQUARE with DJ JuanLove & Pablo Dinámico
DESCRIPTION:🔥🔥SALSA IN THE SQUARE IS BACK!🔥🔥 \n🔥FREE EVENT🔥 \n🔥SALSA IN THE SQUARE🔥 \nwith\nDJ JuanLove❤️\n&\nPablo Dinámico🔥 \nUNION SQUARE\n350 Powell Street\nSan Francisco \n4pm – 8pm\nDJ JuanLove❤️ will keep you moving with the best Cuban Salsa/Timba & Reparto sounds! \n5:30pm\nDance Lesson by Pablo Dinámico🔥\n💥Rumba 💥Timba 💥Reparto \n7pm\nReparto Set Led by Pablo Dinámico🔥 \nDance on a delicious wooden dance floor! \n💥This is a FREE\, Family Friendly Event for All Ages💥 \n💥💥Azucar!💥💥 \n2026 EVENT CALENDAR\n💥From April to October💥\n💥1st Friday of the month:💥 \nSALSA IN THE SQUARE\n5pm – 8pm\n💥April 3rd\n💥May 1st\n💥June 5th\n💥July 3rd\n💥August 7th\n💥September 4th\n💥October 2nd \nUNION SQUARE\n350 Powell Street\nSan Francisco \nTwo blocks from BART (Powell station)\n$6/Hr Parking under the Square \nNot to be missed! \n💥💥Azucar!💥💥 \n#SalsaInTheSquare #DJJuanLove #PabloDinamico #MusicaCubana #Timba #Reparto #UnionSquareSF
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/salsa-in-the-square-with-dj-juanlove-pablo-dinamico/2026-04-03/
LOCATION:Union Square\, San Francisco\, 291 Geary St\, San Francisco\, CA\, United States
CATEGORIES:San Francisco
END:VEVENT
