SUMMARY:¡Baila Bachata! Dance Class & Happy Hour
DESCRIPTION:A brand-new happy hour event with dinner\, drinks\, and bachata dance classes! At NYC’s premier Latin club since 1982. \nGrab a bite\, sip on happy hour cocktails\, and learn to bachata with Arbaaz Mehdi of Piel Canela Dance. \nDoors open at 6:00pm\, dance classes start by 7:00pm\, and entry is FREE w/ RSVP from 6:00-6:30pm (free entry not guaranteed\, subject to venue capacity). Arriving later? Purchase tickets online for priority entry (skip the line) and arrive anytime between 6pm-10pm. \n···· \nFor over 40 years\, SOB’s has been widely known as the premier Latin venue in New York City\, hosting socials with dance lessons\, concerts\, brunches\, post-work happy hours\, & more. Our history with Latin music goes back to the 80’s\, when legends like Celia Cruz\, Tito Puente\, Marc Anthony\, Rubén Blades\, Hector Lavoe\, Willie Colon\, Gilberto Santa Rosa\, and Los Van Van got their start on our stage. \n···· \nTables with drink & dinner service are available on a first-come-first-serve basis. Celebrating something special? Contact manager@sobs.com to find out about our offerings for birthdays\, bachelor/bachelorette parties\, anniversaries\, & more! \n···· \nHave any questions? \nVisit our FAQ \nEmail booking@sobs.com \nCall 212-243-4940 (ext 102)
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/baila-bachata-dance-class-happy-hour/
LOCATION:SOB’s\, 204 Varick St\, New York\, NY\, 10014\, United States
CATEGORIES:New York City
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/BAILA-BACHATA-FLYER-1-scaled-3-1.png
GEO:40.7284492;-74.0051241
X-APPLE-STRUCTURED-LOCATION;VALUE=URI;X-ADDRESS=SOB’s 204 Varick St New York NY 10014 United States;X-APPLE-RADIUS=500;X-TITLE=204 Varick St:geo:-74.0051241,40.7284492
END:VEVENT
