SUMMARY:Caliente Fridays\, Salsa & Bachata at Fulham Pier
DESCRIPTION:Incognito’s brand-new Salsa & Bachata Club is here to Fulham Pier – London’s latest riverside destination. \nCaliente Fridays\, a monthly Salsa & Bachata party night at our BRAND-NEW VENUE\, in the Orange Box\, Fulham Pier \nWith a huge 500 people capacity\, it promises to be one of London’s best Latin nights. \nWe invite you all to come along\, dance\, connect\, and celebrate the launch of our newest Incognito Salsa & Bachata club. \nSCHEDULE \nOpen 7:00 pm \nBACHATA classes at 7:15 – 8:00 pm \nSALSA classes from 8:15 – 9:00 pm \nClasses are available at all levels from Beginners to Advanced.\nParty till 11 pm \nCaliente Fridays –\nSalsa & Bachata Monthly Party Nights\nat Orange Box\, Fulham Pier \nAddress:\nOrange Box (entrance between Doors B & C)\, Fulham Pier\, Stevenage Rd\, SW6 6HH\n(Recommended entrance through the Hammersmith entrance) \nPositioned along the River Thames and nestled in gorgeous parkland with stunning views\, they have transformed this pocket of South-West London into a unique destination. Fulham Pier is also hosting live music\, one-of-a-kind dining\, art exhibitions\, Riverside Market\, and so much more. \nFor more info about Fulham Pier click here \n£15\nClub Entry (Includes FREE Classes) \nBuy Now Incognito Dance \nNo prior bookings are needed\, turn up and dance \nFULL LICENSED BAR.\nAir-Conditioning\nFun & friendly classes for dancers of all levels.\nNo partner is required.\nPlenty of high-quality social dancing to the best and latest Salsa\, Bachata\, Cha-Cha\, Etc.\nAbsolute beginners are warmly welcomed.\nCapacity for 500\nHigh-quality lessons for Beginners to Advanced.\nFun & friendly classes with plenty of high-quality social dancing to the best and latest Salsa\, Bachata\, Cha-Cha\, and Latin grooves.\nRestaurants have many\nfood options.\nWear comfortable shoes and light clothes to keep you dancing comfortably all night\nFREE Parking available on local streets\, close to Putney Bridge Station (7 min walk)\nand Putney Main Line (11 min walk) \nTry our Class & Club Bundle deals below and save money. To buy any of our award-winning courses online for our other venues\, simply click on the course of your choice. The course credits can be used at any of our venues at any time in a 12-month period: \nSalsa & Bachata course for any level: \n3 Class Bundle SALSA BRONZE @ £42\n6 Class Bundle SALSA SILVER @ £78\n9 Class Bundle SALSA GOLD @ £99
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/caliente-fridays-salsa-bachata-at-fulham-pier/2026-04-03/
LOCATION:Fulham Pier\, Fulham Pier\, Stevenage Rd\, SW6 6HH\, United Kingdom
CATEGORIES:London
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/517609852_1306326144835351_8376868823732236236_n.jpg
END:VEVENT
