SUMMARY:Salsa Bachata Classes and Social at The Albion
DESCRIPTION:FREE Salsa & Bachata classes every Friday at The Albion in South Melbourne! \nFREE Latin dance classes and social dancing  as the pre-party to the Oye Latino Reggaeton night EVERY FRIDAY at The Albion Rooftop & Club! \n172 York Street South Melbourne \n6:45pm Doors open. Come in for a drink & meet the other students \n7pm Salsa classes levels 1 & 2\n8pm Bachata classes levels 1 & 2 \nFirst-timers welcome! \n9pm Salsa & Bachata social dancing until about 10:15pm \n10:15pm the Reggaeton DJs start the Oye Latino party and play a mix of Latin hits until 4 or 5am! \n10:30pm head upstairs to the rooftop for more Bachata & Salsa mixed in with some Latin favourites\, Reggaeton\, Afrobeats\, R&B and more! \nFREE ENTRY ALL NIGHT! \nTickets are not compulsory but it does help us manage male & female ratios for the dance classes and so the venue knows how many staff they need! \nPlease arrive early for classes! \nFollow us to find out about our other Bachata & Salsa classes and parties throughout the week!
URL:https://golatindance.com/event/free-salsa-bachata-classes-and-social-dancing-every-friday-2-2/2026-04-03/
LOCATION:The Albion Rooftop & Club\, 172 York Street\, Melbourne\, 3205\, Australia
CATEGORIES:Melbourne
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://golatindance.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/204201_image_348972622_1382328022331969_6847795088042958896_n.jpg
END:VEVENT
